<plot>A teen girl (Angela Bettis) enjoying a rare free weekend from her religious parents is suddenly confronted by a young Mexican intruder (Douglas Spain), who randomly chose her house to hide out. Seems he was badly beaten by two local thugs in a racially motivated attack and he took his revenge on the two. This put him on the run from the local bigoted sheriff (William Lucking). Slowly the two reveal their emotional baggage and become genuinely attracted to one another.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?569198</url></doc>
